Key Match Events: Guerschon Yabusele came up with a key block on a Bilal Coulibaly driving layup attempt and then nailed two clutch free throws to secure a 76ers victory over the Wizards.
Post-Match Reflections: Yabusele's energetic style of play and ability were evident, scoring 20 points, and throwing down a dunk over LeBron James that quickly went viral.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The 76ers have battled injuries all season in their frontcourt, most notably to Joel Embiid, but also to Andre Drummond.
